commitResults.messageBody:
Add a JavaFX GUI to my Cicada chatbot. Change the display methods
to return String.

commitResults.messageTitle: Update build.gradle file to generate JAR file
commitResults.messageBody:
Change the mainClass to duke.Launcher for generating JAR file for this
new JavaFX GUI. Comment out the JUnit tests as now it is no longer
Text-UI based, and the methods have been modified for the JavaFX GUI
already.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add assertions to Duke and MainWindow class
commitResults.messageBody:
Use assert feature to document some important assumptions made in
the Duke class and MainWindow class. I was stuck at null Ui object
for previous task, hence I assert Ui != null in the Duke class.

commitResults.messageTitle: Shorten prepareCreateEvent() method in Parser class
commitResults.messageBody:
Create isTaskArgumentBlank() and convertToLocalDateTime() method in Parser class
to shorten line of codes and following the code quality guideline of no more than
30 lines of code for a method.

commitResults.messageTitle: Shorten parse() method in Parser class
commitResults.messageBody:
Convert the handling of each command word into individual methods
so that the line of codes for this method will be within 30 lines.

commitResults.messageTitle: Shorten load() method in Storage class
commitResults.messageBody:
Convert part of code in load() to a new method called addTaskToList()
to shorten the line of codes in load() method as is exceeds 30 lines.
Change the code structure of load() to minimise deep nesting.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Utils method to put common methods
commitResults.messageBody:
Add Utils class to put common methods so that these methods
can be used among different classes.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Javadoc for all classes
commitResults.messageBody: Add JavaDoc for all methods and classes.
